org.afplib.afplib

Interface PTD1

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PTD1Impl

    public interface PTD1
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'PTD1'.

    The following features are supported:

    • XPBASE
    • YPBASE
    • XPUNITVL
    • YPUNITVL
    • XPEXTENT
    • YPEXTENT
    • RESERVED

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getPTD1()
